snippet.title: Among Us 3D - NEW Mode Teaser | FGS LIVE FROM GDC
snippet.description:
Just announced at FGS Live From GDC, Infected is the new mode for Among US 3D, a first-person party game of deception. Among Us 3D is playable now on Steam.  
https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #amongus3d #gdc

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
